Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:13.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I wish the mailpony would just come already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:17.57,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I can't wait another minute to find out if Rainbow Dash got in or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:20.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, you're more nervous than Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:22.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm not nervous at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:24.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,When I get into the Wonderbolt Academy…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:25.72,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,If you get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:27.34,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,IF you get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:28.49,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Don't jinx it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:30.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's in the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:31.87,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Don't jinx it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:34.08,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She is the best flyer in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:36.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,In Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:40.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm probably the best flier in all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:42.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised if they just went ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:45.16,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and made me a Wonderbolt on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.29,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Got a letter here for Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:53.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I didn't get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:57.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:01.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You guys are so gullible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Like I wasn't gonna get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:08.42,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'm just sooooooooooo happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:11.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:14.64,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:16.64,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I kinda need to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:20.57,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:25.01,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The sooner I get there, the sooner I get to show them my stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.20,0:01:27.63,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,See you guys in a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:28.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:30.66,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Won't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:36.49,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,DON'T FORGET TO WRITE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:42.41,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Do you think she heard me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! This is gonna be sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.73,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Well lookie what we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.98,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Bet y'all think you're Wonderbolt material, don't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:02.98,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.93,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Think you got what it takes to be an elite flyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.33,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.40,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Well then. Let me be the first to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:12.51,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,YOU DON'T!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:14.72,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,If you had what it took to be an elite flyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:16.72,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,you'd already be a Wonderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:20.13,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Still think you're something special?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:22.16,Somepony,,0,0,0,,No ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:32.36,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Ya think you're hot stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.89,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,You look like you're the worst flyer in the whole academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:39.26,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,You'll probably quit after the first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No ma'am! I'd never quit, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.06,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:48.51,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Bet you couldn't fly past the first flagpole without getting winded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:50.20,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Try me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.20,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.94,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Let me show you what I've got, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.37,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,You want a chance to prove yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.55,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.62,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Well then, now's your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.30,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Give me five hundred laps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.60,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:05.74,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.94,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Lap four-hundred and ninety-nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,One more lap to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:25.92,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,You're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:35.48,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Five hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.29,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:42.46,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,For a couple of newbies…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.03,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Name's Lightning Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:46.97,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Wanna grab some grub in the mess hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:47.97,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:59.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, Rainbow Dash hasn't even been gone twenty-four hours yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Give her a chance to settle in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.86,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just go see what Twilight's up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:06.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I hear Princess Celestia's got her working on some new spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.78,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,New spells, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.78,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.41,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,If I'm not here when Rainbow Dash's letter arrives,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.24,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to read it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:18.24,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And if I don't read it right away, I won't be able to write her back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:20.85,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And if I don't write her back right away, she might think I didn't get her letter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and then she might worry it got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.99,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and if she's worried about her letter she'll get distracted,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.85,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and if she's distracted then she won't do well at the academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:28.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and if she doesn't do well at the academy, then she'll get kicked out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:30.29,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and if she gets kicked out, she'll never be allowed to be a Wonderbolt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:34.25,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and if she doesn't get to be a Wonderbolt, all her dreams will be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.77,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And it will be all…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:36.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,my…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:37.89,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,FAULT!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:42.11,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,So in other words, you're stickin' by the mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.02,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:44.32,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:54.34,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts are the fastest, best precision flyers in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:56.68,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,But spinouts can still happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:00.58,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,And when they do, a Wonderbolt must be able to recover quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:01.38,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,This…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.74,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,is the Dizzitron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:07.22,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,It's gonna make you very, I repeat, very dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:10.31,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Your task is to try and recover, and fly straight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:12.04,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,As soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:14.71,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Once you have recovered you must come in for a smooth landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:16.79,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Now, who's first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:17.79,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:19.75,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,You're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.75,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.04,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:31.35,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.22,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.12,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:46.75,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.70,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Fifteen seconds. Decent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:06.57,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't go writin' home about it! Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.21,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,All right, Rainbow Dash. Let's see what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.21,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:14.32,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Okay, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:20.96,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.83,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Six seconds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.33,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,That's an academy record.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:32.21,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You made it look so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:35.21,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I make everything look easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.21,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Okay Lightning Dust, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:41.25,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, can you put the Dizzitron at maximum speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.25,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,I wanna push my limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.61,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.61,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.33,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Okay. You asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:04.35,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:13.37,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Six point five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.37,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.00,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,NEXT!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:26.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No pony even came close to six seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:29.06,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,They should make us Wonderbolts right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:30.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah they should!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:32.06,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:34.20,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,For the rest of the camp, you'll be working in pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:37.45,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,'Morrow morning I'll post the teams including who'll be lead pony,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.92,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,and who'll be wing pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:39.92,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.35,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Like we're going to need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:43.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Heh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:52.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, which one of you lucky gals gets to be my wing pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:54.96,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:56.96,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You might want to check the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:03.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,A wing pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.95,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,They made us a team! Isn't that awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Permission to enter, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.88,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,What is it Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:27.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I had the best time on the Dizzitron! Only six seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.39,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And you made me a wing pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:38.29,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Because I believe you and Lightning Dust will be an unstoppable team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.54,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Do you not think you'll be an unstoppable team?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:41.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I mean, no ma'am! I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:46.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We'll be an unstoppable team, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:48.03,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Then what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I think I should be lead pony, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:56.41,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,And I think Lightning Dust likes to push herself a little harder than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:59.29,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,That's why I made her lead pony. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:01.81,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:02.62,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:18.32,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Today you will all be participating in the flag hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.95,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,We'll divide you into two teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.20,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Red,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.00,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,and blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:27.91,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Whoever finds the most flags of the opposing team's color wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.56,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is gonna be so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.74,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,If you think this is going to be fun, you are sadly mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.52,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,This is for training purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.15,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,This is not recess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.63,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Lead ponies and wing ponies must fly together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.64,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,If any pair splits apart, they will be immediately disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.55,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:48.87,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.34,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.23,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Ready to rock and roll?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.87,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,You spotted any flags yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:15.64,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh! There's one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:19.32,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Good eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.58,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We should slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like both of us can make it at this speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:36.63,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Lightning Dust and Rainbow Dash found the first flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:41.16,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's find some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:44.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sure. Just give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.03,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah… totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.64,Rarity,,0,0,0,,She's still at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:05.94,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I just wish we could help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:09.99,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Help me? The only thing that could possibly help me is a letter from Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's been three days already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.86,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,By now, she probably doesn't even know our names anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:17.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,She probably can't remember our faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:21.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"Pinkie Pie? I never heard of a Pinkie Pie! Who is Pinkie Pie?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:25.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well if you're so worried, then why don't you send her a letter first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:29.08,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Of course! That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.59,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh wait! I got an even better idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:35.24,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,How about we send Rainbow Dash a care package?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.31,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You know, before she forgets all about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:40.64,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Although, come on, let's face it. It's probably too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:43.08,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But uh, maybe it'll jog her memory somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:47.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, I'm sure Rainbow Dash still remembers our faces and who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I think sending her a care package is a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.21,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,A care package it is! We'll send it through the mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.82,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,WAIT! Ah! That won't work at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:57.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:00.25,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Because what if the package gets lost in the mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.14,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,What if somepony else gets the package by accident
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:04.17,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and then she remembers us instead of Rainbow Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.45,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and she becomes our new friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:10.39,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and then the real Rainbow Dash wouldn't ever know that she used to have friends and she forgot them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Is anypony else following this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:14.69,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:17.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We'll deliver the care package to Rainbow Dash in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind a little trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:19.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:20.94,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:21.82,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.78,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Me five!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But don't be upset if she doesn't recognize you at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It may take a while for her to get her memory back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.29,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Today we'll be doing our famous air obstacle course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:48.17,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,The object of this exercise is to work on your precision flying under extreme circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.02,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,And don't worry about winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.47,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,It's not a race.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.06,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Now everypony, get on your marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.77,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Can't they go any faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.71,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,It's no good, I can't get around them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:27.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:31.98,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We can still fly completely in sync and blow Spitfire's mind with our moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:33.63,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.54,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,What are they, a couple of snails?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.99,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,It's just a little weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.03,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance to pass these slowpokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:10.71,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.23,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,And in record time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:14.81,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Definitely made the right decision making you two a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:19.81,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,The others seem to have had a little trouble with the precision part of the exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:21.49,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,I'd better go help sort them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.64,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Why don't you two go hit the mess hall early?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:24.68,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:26.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thank you ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Lightning Dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:32.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Next time, maybe we don't cut the other teams off like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.85,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Hey, you snooze, you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:38.73,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Besides, Wonderbolts are supposed to be able to recover from a spinout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.72,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,You saw them on the Dizzitron!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.63,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,They could use the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:46.24,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not our fault we're so much better than those other guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.66,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Not every pony is destined to become a Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.72,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Only the best of the best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess you're right…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.84,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,'Course I'm right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:16:00.64,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Now let's go fuel up! Kicking all that tail has made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:27.42,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:40.70,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,I have an idea about how we can literally blow away our competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:45.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But we're already way ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.94,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Are you in, or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.17,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lightning Dust likes to push herself a little harder than you do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.30,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I made her lead pony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:56.93,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Then follow my lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.90,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,I can't control it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.37,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's a twister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Noooooo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:11.81,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:17.50,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You… remember me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:21.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well yeah, of course I remember you! But what are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:24.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We wanted to bring you a care package.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:27.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Didn't realize you'd be in the middle of some crazy tornado drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:30.22,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,That… was… Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,My friends could have been smashed to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.86,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but they weren't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.06,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Can't say the same for the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:41.67,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,We totally wiped them out with that tornado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:45.22,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,The other cadets will have to be up there for days to bust as many as we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,A hoof bump? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You made me clip my wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:54.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You sent half of our class into serious tail spins on the obstacle course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:58.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You unleashed a tornado that nearly demolished my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.76,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:02.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And I get that you want to be the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So do I!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:06.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But you're going about it in the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.75,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts don't seem to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:13.42,Lighting Dust,,0,0,0,,After all, Spitfire did make me the leader and you the wing pony and you the wing pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.16,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.91,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,This better be important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:24.72,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be up there busting clouds with your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're done with that, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:28.42,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Already? That's an academy record!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.03,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Explain your methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Lightning Dust decided to use a tornado.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.94,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,A bit excessive for cloud-busting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:39.10,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,But judging from your time, it was obviously an effective tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:42.91,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well that "effective tactic" nearly took out my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.54,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No disrespect ma'am,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:47.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,but there's a big difference between pushing yourself has hard as you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:49.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and just being reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And if being reckless is what gets rewarded around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:56.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,if that's what it means to be a Wonderbolt, then I don't want any part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:19:58.87,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, newbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Being a Wonderbolt was your dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know how much this meant to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.02,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:29.28,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,How dare you storm out of my office without giving me a chance to respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.69,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts are looking for the best flyers in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:36.58,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,You were right. Being the best should never come at the expense of our fellow ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.99,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,It's not just about pushing ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.73,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,It's about pushing ourselves in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.68,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,You've shown that you're capable of doing just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.34,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,You're no wing pony, Rainbow Dash,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:02.76,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,you're a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:12.64,Spitfire,,0,0,0,,Now get out there and give me twenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:13.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:26.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:29.58,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You didn't even get to open your care package!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:33.97,Somepony,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVIY PONETS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:37.97,Somepony,,0,0,0,,anon2anon \N sunnysubs.com
